name: WO - Remain Qty
query:
SELECT woi.parent as "Work Order:Link/Work Order:150",
    wo.production_item as "Item to Mfg:Link/Item:110",
    woi.item_code as "Item Code:Link/Item:110",
    woi.item_name as "Item Name:Data:300",
    wo.modified as "Modified:Date:130",
    woi.remains_qty as "Remain Qty:Float:100",
    sle.batch_no as "Batch:Data:100"
    from `tabWork Order` wo INNER JOIN `tabWork Order Item` woi ON woi.parent = wo.name INNER JOIN 
    `tabStock Ledger Entry` sle ON wo.project = sle.project WHERE woi.remains_qty > 0.01 AND woi.item_code = sle.item_code
    GROUP BY sle.batch_no
